<tr id="L10"><td><a href="#L10">10</a></td><td>SPOCK:  Absolutely none, Captain. Berthold rays are such a recent discovery. We do not yet have full knowledge of their nature. It is known, however, that living animal tissue disintegrates under exposure. Sandoval's group could not have survived after three years.</td></tr>

<tr id="L11"><td><a href="#L11">11</a></td><td>KIRK:  Are you saying that those people built a future in a place knowing they might not survive?</td></tr>

